meta.title: WAsn5-92
meta.author: Vladimir Batagelj
meta.desc: We collected from WoS the hits for queries SO=(SOCIAL NETWORKS) +  SO=("social network*"+ most frequent references + around 100 social networkers. The final collection of networks has: |W| = 193376; |C| = 7950; |A| = 75930; |J| = 14651; |K| = 29267. These data was named SN5 and was used as a data set for Sunbelt 2008 Viszards session.

meta.title: SN92
meta.author: Vladimir Batagelj
meta.desc: We identified 92 most active researchers in SN5, extracted the corresponding subnetworks, and transformed them into Ianus temporal networks.
